snippet.title: Super Mario Bros. theme played on wine glasses
snippet.description: This ultimate tribute to Mario, Luigi, Princess Peach, Toad, and Yoshi uses drinking glasses, pencils, and even a frying pan to play the iconic theme song.

snippet.title: Beats Music (iOS)
snippet.description: We go hands-on with Beats' new premium music service, designed to appeal to people who want a more automated music listening experience.

snippet.title: Google Play Music for iOS
snippet.description: With a streaming library that won't fill up your iPhone storage in the free version, along with excellent music discovery options and ad-free radio with All Access, Google Play Music is a great option for audiophiles.

snippet.title: Archos aims for music lovers with the dualcore 40B Titanium
snippet.description: The Archos 40B Titanium may not have the most high-end features, but dual speakers promise a tuneful listening experience.

snippet.title: Xbox Music for Android
snippet.description: Xbox Music feels more like a first foray into music streaming rather than a finished product; it's functional, but it needs more features to compare with established apps like Spotify.

snippet.title: Xbox Music for iPhone
snippet.description: Xbox Music feels more like a first foray into music streaming rather than a finished product; it's functional, but it needs more features to compare with established apps like Spotify.

snippet.title: Heavy methal: 'Breaking Bad' theme played on meth lab gear
snippet.description: Musician Andrew Huang performs a one-man cover of the "Breaking Bad" theme song using equipment one would find in a meth lab.

snippet.title: 'Anchorman' news team recounts year in Yahoo searches
snippet.description: In this video, actor Will Ferrell and friends "report" on the year in Yahoo searches, reprising their roles from the film and its upcoming sequel.

snippet.title: AwoX StriimLight B-10
snippet.description: The StriimLight B-10 and StriimLight Wi-Fi are LEDs with integrated speakers that let you adjust music volume and bulb brightness from your couch.

snippet.title: Burning Man's 2014 theme: Caravansary
snippet.description: The annual arts festival says its 2014 theme will be "a bazaar of the bizarre." And for the first time since 1997, the Man will rise from the desert floor.
